---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import { getContent } from '../lib/content';
const content = await getContent();
---
<Base title="Safety & Terms" description="The short version of how Denver Social works.">
<div class="c-page">

  <header class="c-hero">
    <div class="c-tag">Safety & Terms</div>
    <h1 class="c-title" set:html={content.conduct_title}></h1>
    <p class="c-lede">The short version.</p>
  </header>

  <ol class="c-rules">
    <li class="c-rule">
      <span class="c-num">👋</span>
      <div>
        <h2>Everyone's welcome.</h2>
        <p>Quiet, loud, awkward, neurodivergent, brand new to Denver — you're good here. Leave whenever you want. You don't owe anyone an explanation. 🚪</p>
      </div>
    </li>

    <li class="c-rule">
      <span class="c-num">🔒</span>
      <div>
        <h2>Your info stays private.</h2>
        <p>Locations and host phone numbers are hidden until you RSVP. Other members only see your first name and neighborhood. No data selling, no creep tracking.</p>
      </div>
    </li>

    <li class="c-rule">
      <span class="c-num">🎤</span>
      <div>
        <h2>Hosts are accountable.</h2>
        <p>Every event has a named host. Events get a quick moderation pass before going live. Groups stay small (usually 6–12 people) so things actually feel like a hangout.</p>
      </div>
    </li>

    <li class="c-rule c-rule-warn">
      <span class="c-num c-num-warn">🚫</span>
      <div>
        <h2>What gets you removed.</h2>
        <p>Harassment, intimidation, following someone after an event, or sharing someone's location or private info. You don't need proof to report — your word is enough. We listen, we act.</p>
      </div>
    </li>

    <li class="c-rule">
      <span class="c-num">📣</span>
      <div>
        <h2>Report anything that feels off.</h2>
        <p>Tell the host on the spot, jump in our Discord, or email us. We keep it between us. No "are you sure?" gauntlet.</p>
        <div class="c-btns">
          <a href="https://discord.gg/S8SFNkdSgK" class="c-btn c-btn-discord" target="_blank" rel="noopener">💬 Discord</a>
          <a href="/contact" class="c-btn c-btn-ghost">✉️ Contact us</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </li>

    <li class="c-rule">
      <span class="c-num">🎉</span>
      <div>
        <h2>It's free, and that's the deal.</h2>
        <p>No fees, no premium tier, no upsell. Some events have venue costs between you and the venue — we don't take a cut. Denver Social organizes the meetups but isn't liable for what happens at them. Show up, have fun, be cool. 🏔</p>
      </div>
    </li>
  </ol>

  <p class="c-updated">Last updated March 2026 · <a href="/events">See what's coming up →</a></p>

</div>

<style is:inline>
  .c-page { max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 32px clamp(20px, 4vw, 40px) 96px; }

  .c-hero { padding: 16px 0 40px; }
  .c-tag {
    display: inline-block; font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent); background: var(--accent-dim);
    padding: 6px 14px; border-radius: 999px; margin-bottom: 18px;
  }
  .c-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: clamp(34px, 5vw, 48px); font-weight: 900;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em; line-height: 1.1; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .c-title em { font-style: normal; color: var(--accent); }
  .c-lede { font-size: 17px; color: var(--text-sec); }

  .c-rules { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 14px; }
  .c-rule {
    display: flex; gap: 18px; align-items: flex-start;
    padding: 22px clamp(18px, 3vw, 26px);
    background: var(--bg); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 16px;
    transition: border-color 0.15s, transform 0.15s;
  }
  .c-rule:hover { border-color: var(--border-hover); transform: translateY(-1px); }
  .c-rule h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 19px; font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .c-rule p { font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; color: var(--text-sec); }
  .c-num {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 44px; height: 44px; border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 22px;
    background: var(--accent-dim);
  }
  .c-rule-warn { background: linear-gradient(180deg, #FEF2F2, #fff); border-color: #FECACA; }
  .c-num-warn { background: #FEE2E2; }

  .c-btns { display: flex; gap: 10px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 14px; }
  .c-btn {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 999px;
    font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700;
    text-decoration: none; transition: transform 0.15s, box-shadow 0.15s, background 0.15s;
  }
  .c-btn-discord { background: #5865F2; color: #fff; }
  .c-btn-discord:hover { transform: translateY(-1px); box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(88,101,242,0.32); }
  .c-btn-ghost { background: var(--surface); color: var(--text); border: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .c-btn-ghost:hover { background: var(--surface-hover); }

  .c-updated {
    margin-top: 36px; font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-faint); text-align: center;
  }
  .c-updated a { color: var(--accent); font-weight: 600; }
</style>
</Base>
